"What talking is for Gather the pieces, so I can show you what is. That's what talking is for, to help us be one. Many-ness is having sixty different emotions. Unity is peace and silence. I know I ought to stop now, but the excitement of this keeps opening my mouth like a sneeze or a yawn does. Muhammad says, I ask forgiveness seventy times a day, and I do the same. Forgive my talking so much, but the way God makes mysteries manifest quickens and keeps the flow of words continual." ,
